      "comment": "HEAVY HAULAGE (4) is a well performed dog and winner of 10 races who was in the minor money last time out at Ballarat (25.49). Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Makes plenty of appeal. TRIBECA (5) was seventh in a Special conditions race two back then found trouble in the run and took a tumble at Shepparton last time. Has the ability and looks a key chance. AGENT SUSIE (2) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts two wins and three placings. Missed the frame latest (23.31) when seventh over 400m at Warragul in a Grade 4/5. Among the main chances. FLAMING FOX (8) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
